OL,3,CBergerac old and new: John Nettles
OL,4,Cmeets Damien Molony as show returns
OL,6,FThe star of the modern re-imagining of
OL,7,FBergerac has said he does not believe
OL,8,Fthe series could be set anywhere other
OL,9,Fthan Jersey.
OL,11,FDamien Molony, who plays iconic island
OL,12,Fdetective Jim Bergerac in the reboot,
OL,13,Freflected on the importance of the
OL,14,Fsetting in conversation with his
OL,15,Fpredecessor John Nettles.
OL,17,FHe explained: "The setting is a
OL,18,Fcharacter all in itself.
