OL,6,F"The fact that it's an island means
OL,7,Fthere's an added tension for the
OL,8,Fpolice force - you have to catch the
OL,9,Fkiller before they get off the island."
OL,11,FNettles agreed, adding the island's
OL,12,Fsmall size also plays a role.
OL,14,FHe recalled: "I do remember John
OL,15,FSessions saying to me, 'I don't know
OL,16,Fwhy you bother to chase all the
OL,17,Fthieves in Jersey. Why don't you just
OL,18,Fstay in one point? They're bound to
OL,19,Fcome around again eventually'."
