OL,3,CBergerac old and new: John Nettles
OL,4,Cmeets Damien Molony as show returns
OL,6,FThe two met ahead of the new series
OL,7,Fbeing premiered in Jersey on Monday 24
OL,8,FFebruary.
OL,10,FTheir conversation also covered what
OL,11,Ffans of the old show, which ran for a
OL,12,Fdecade in the 1980s, could expect to
OL,13,Fsee in the new adaptation.
OL,15,FThe detective's classic look remains
OL,16,Funchanged: Jim Bergerac will once
OL,17,Fagain don a leather jacket and drive
OL,18,Fhis famous red Triumph Roadster.
