OL,6,FHowever, Damien Moloney said that
OL,7,Fwhilst the car in the new series is
OL,8,Fthe same as the original, he was not
OL,9,Fallowed to get behind the wheel.
OL,11,FMolony told Nettles: "I didn't drive
OL,12,Fit, I really wanted to drive it but I
OL,13,Fdon't think insurance got anywhere
OL,14,Fnear allowing me to drive that car.
OL,16,F"The car is so special, it has a
OL,17,Fwonderful symbolism in our series.
