OL,6,F"People who loved the original
OL,7,FBergerac will spot all of these kind
OL,8,Fof wonderful references to the
OL,9,Foriginal."
OL,11,FDamien Molony will star in the new
OL,12,Fseries alongside Zoe Wanamaker and
OL,13,FPhilip Glenister who appeared in the
OL,14,Foriginal series' final episode.
OL,16,FThe show has been directed by Colm
OL,17,FMcCarthy, known for his work on Peaky
OL,18,FBlinders, Sherlock, and Endeavour.
